INSERT INTO purchases (customerName, customerEmail, customerPhone, campaignName, campaignSlug, planType, amountPaid, currency, status, isTrial, trialSignupId, plainPassword, expiresAt, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT name, email, whatsapp, campaignName, campaignSlug, '2_months', 0, 'BRL', 'completed', true, id, plainPassword, expiresAt, createdAt, updatedAt 
FROM trial_signups 
WHERE campaignSlug = 'guilherme';
